{"tid":333374,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"阿媽話去澳門三日兩夜齋留酒店係咩心態","createTime":"2017-07-23T17:54:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T12:35:13.000Z","uid":28802,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f66fd5d2295888b37a4c559b012dd4f6097cdc4f","tid":333374,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:54:21.000Z","msg":"早兩日阿媽同我講<br />\n話下星期去澳門 仲話會帶埋佢啲師奶朋友去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我咪問佢無端端去澳門做乜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話啲朋友向佢介紹左新壕天地有個特價plan想去<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">玩</span>幾日 但個plan都唔平下 一位都要4500幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我再問我阿媽 果幾日會做啲咩<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢同我講淨係stay喺酒店入面</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啫係咁 去澳門唔係問題 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">但佢又唔賭錢嘅 </span><br />\n又話去澳門玩但又淨係stay酒店揼下骨游下水咁<br />\n酒店個商場又唔算好行 野又貴好多 又多蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔肯去下城區果啲地方食下地道野<br />\n原因竟然係嫌等啲shuttle bus耐同麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新壕天地嗰邊舊年都去過 完全唔覺有咩特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說佢都幾鍾意旅遊<br />\n咁我咪即刻同佢講依家飛台灣玩三四日都抵仲啦 <br />\n佢竟然say no<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我真係好想知道去澳門三日兩夜齋留酒店係咩心態</span>"},{"pid":"a4c1a71fc6494e4a2a4626662499bb4a8cf11891","tid":333374,"uid":7628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:56:43.000Z","msg":"ptm?"},{"pid":"85744cb7cbcf0e4a432eaf1c8b4afbe6bc34aabe","tid":333374,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:59:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ptm?</blockquote><br />\n唔係咁開心呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"039d7875a0a6abca76205c1f8a01c2e64670a842","tid":333374,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:00:24.000Z","msg":"住酒店香港都有啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba5ced72c9235a0add1fc4c67d3510ada34cfbb","tid":333374,"uid":68081,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:01:30.000Z","msg":"你老母想食鴨唔通又要話你知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847b69f307f9f1ec000ea0abb3fbbd865308e354","tid":333374,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:02:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>住酒店香港都有啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 咪就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲有三日兩夜4500<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住自己行下城區 又話我唔跟大隊 話掃興喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"478f658a194fc41afffc02d26ddd8f4d78b767bf","tid":333374,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:02:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你老母想食鴨唔通又要話你知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e13a493e2ef0b31a86fc08aa12effcfc3f833a","tid":333374,"uid":72902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:04:11.000Z","msg":"其實酒店唔係姐係賭場咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b762e101c49cb55f6191874c5849285e01c09e","tid":333374,"uid":40337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:04:38.000Z","msg":"公道講句<br />\n你老母去澳門俾佬屌"},{"pid":"86a3743cd7fb66d54887db4cdd0ad90529e88f82","tid":333374,"uid":58911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:08:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你老母想食鴨唔通又要話你知<img src=\